# TODO

# Examples:

```C
...
int max = 10;
int result = 0;
for (int i = 0; i < max; i++) {
    result++;
}
return result;
```

Simplifies to:

```C
int max = 10;
int result = 0;
for (; result < max; result++) {}
return result;
```